query:
CREATE TABLE viability_analysis (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  nome VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  valorCaptacao INT NOT NULL,
  coInvestimento INT NOT NULL,
  feeFixo INT NOT NULL,
  taxaSucesso INT NOT NULL,
  taxaJurosMensal INT NOT NULL,
  prazoMeses INT NOT NULL,
  carenciaMeses INT NOT NULL,
  modeloPagamento ENUM('SAC', 'PRICE', 'BULLET') NOT NULL,
  capexObras INT NOT NULL,
  capexEquipamentos INT NOT NULL,
  capexLicencas INT NOT NULL,
  capexMarketing INT NOT NULL,
  capexCapitalGiro INT NOT NULL,
  capexOutros INT NOT NULL,
  opexAluguel INT NOT NULL,
  opexPessoal INT NOT NULL,
  opexRoyalties INT NOT NULL,
  opexMarketing INT NOT NULL,
  opexUtilidades INT NOT NULL,
  opexManutencao INT NOT NULL,
  opexSeguros INT NOT NULL,
  opexOutros INT NOT NULL,
  ticketMedio INT NOT NULL,
  capacidadeMaxima INT NOT NULL,
  mesAbertura INT NOT NULL,
  clientesInicio INT NOT NULL,
  taxaCrescimento INT NOT NULL,
  mesEstabilizacao INT NOT NULL,
  clientesSteadyState INT NOT NULL,
  fluxoCaixa TEXT,
  indicadores TEXT,
  status ENUM('em_analise', 'viavel', 'inviavel') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'em_analise',
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX user_idx (userId),
  INDEX status_idx (status)
)
